    • getCallNoneToReturnFlowFunction

      public IUnaryFlowFunction getCallNoneToReturnFlowFunction(BasicBlockInContext<E> src, BasicBlockInContext<E> dest)
      Specified by:
      getCallNoneToReturnFlowFunction in interface IFlowFunctionMap<E extends ISSABasicBlock>
      Returns:
      the flow function for a "call-to-return" edge in the supergraph from src -> dest, when the supergraph does not contain any callees of src. This happens via, e.g., slicing.
